metadata.name: Perception
metadata.description:
Where are we ? Where are you ? from the outer reaches of the universe to the darkest depths of the ocean, our perception is tricked by the elements, the lights and our ability to understand.

Deep down we are lost, looking for signs and reason to be. But there is a light.


By Livio Fakeye
